 Final Correct File Structure
resources/views/admin/

dashboard.blade.php  → layout

unverified.blade.php → child
verified.blade.php   → child
inactive.blade.php   → child

Child files must only contain:

@extends
@section
@endsection

NOT full HTML.

 Why Sidebar Moves

Because browser reads:

dashboard.html
   └ unverified.html (another html page inside)

So CSS flex layout breaks → sidebar shifts.
